verse = \lyricmode {
  Be -- fore the break of day I cry to you;
your word I trust, for you are my de -- fen -- der.
I e -- ven lie a -- wake the whole night through,
that I your stead -- fast prom -- is -- es may pon -- der.
LORD, in your righ -- teous -- ness my life re -- new;
hear me and show your love and mer -- cy ten -- der.
}
